<br>
To make word bubbles:<br>
<br>
- Make an oval selection and fill it.<br>
- Make a triangle pointingto the character by using the lasso selection tool and fill it with the same colour.<br>
- Use the magic wand to select the word-bubble shape and go to select &gt; modify &gt; border. Type down a border size.<br>
- Get the paint bucket tool to fill the border selection. <p>---<br>
